{"tid":1614371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依個時候魔攻先係最有效嘅攻擊","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T18:40:03.000Z","uid":298795,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"55027b94c77a773c688a0a3dac3a528025f8d357","tid":1614371,"uid":298795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:26:32.000Z","msg":"到左依個時候已經係好明顯<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗係絕對唔會吝嗇任何可以殺人嘅機會</span></span><br />\n睇撚住佢對準手足嘅左胸開槍，根本嗰一刻嘅用意係好純粹，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係想殺人。</span><br />\n<br />\n但事實上我地嘅物攻物防係唔夠對面高攻，唔可以再犧牲任何一位手足賣肉擋攻擊，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以我地一定要出魔攻裝</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">水魔法同火魔法就唔洗講</span><br />\n借Post<br />\n火魔法防禦學 及 水魔法進攻學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612376</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陷阱魔法</span><br />\n對狗專用。新魔法師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613675</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有咁上下就用蟲系魔法</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPKJh7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPKJh7a.png&h=7f1a0187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">適當時候結界師</span><br />\n已解鎖技能：鎖鏈結界<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614060</a><br />\n<br />\n魔攻嘅特性就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">牽制敵人，消耗對手。</span><br />\n唔好再賣肉我求下你地，一個都嫌多。<br />\n<br />\n最後P牌仔求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381eb40cdb303e0b577d20bd63416aa70d866eb1","tid":1614371,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:27:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a921a5533350227d08efb0e72f1b34b53832c783","tid":1614371,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"其實蟲蟲攻擊大概幾錢一次"},{"pid":"65194941235392390b251ed54af4a03923042a6b","tid":1614371,"uid":172833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:27:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dc209cafb7c8a95ad456e21204f71051fc176c","tid":1614371,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:28:39.000Z","msg":"仲有強光電筒魔法<br />\n同埋<br />\n水槍配電油/油漆魔法"},{"pid":"276530d54055f01528f120fa37b3d84c1e76eef2","tid":1614371,"uid":231178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a921a5533350227d08efb0e72f1b34b53832c783","tid":1614371,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"其實蟲蟲攻擊大概幾錢一次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:29:49.000Z","msg":"睇下你一次過汁到幾多？蟲蟲唔係咁易玩"},{"pid":"1e75d7f3d0480d89711369a453d67656cc0eaef0","tid":1614371,"uid":8880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a921a5533350227d08efb0e72f1b34b53832c783","tid":1614371,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"其實蟲蟲攻擊大概幾錢一次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:40:03.000Z","msg":"執幾隻養 好快成箱都係"}]}